/lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"d610381c503890c471e5d5d4f20348fb7675f1ae","tid":1667982,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af80c845e52668a7399f8bd90774f4129a6c45cd","tid":1667982,"uid":30563,"like":157,"dislike":1,"score":156,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"係屋企等啲差佬死哂先<br />\n之後再落街打老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"1e05c427b3e2eb0d01e302335e51434ec1de9c5b","tid":1667982,"uid":268123,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"我驚警察搞掂咗老解"},{"pid":"8c87ae8e0cb83cdaa65f25e0f8f70f53906f34fe","tid":1667982,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b588722833bf8b7ee1b1987661ee679fe05e48d7","tid":1667982,"uid":188922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0682a9cd51491f662533c10891a86ebd97d7538","tid":1667982,"uid":37869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c1c80acbc43d360b75c670b1b58d8b829c8bf29c","tid":1667982,"uid":132030,